<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> نَزَلْتُ فِي أهل الشّرك خَاصَّة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>